        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Like the host of God, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " i.e. innumerable, like the stars or angels, both which are called God’s hosts. Otherwise, ",
