        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "the host of God",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", i.e. a very great host, great things being so called, as ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "cedars, mountains, &c. of God",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". But the particle of likeness here added excludes this sense, for it had been very improper to say, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "a great host like a great host",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", i.e. like itself. ",
        "children": []
